Output Format MUST BE exactly JSON:
{
  "headline": "...",
  "slug": "...",
  "keywords": ["...", "..."]
}' }}

={{ 'You are Agent Beta, a Senior Quantitative Analyst. Read the raw news:

' + $node["Parse XML & Select Top 3"].json["content"] + '

Extract all hard data, numbers, quotes, and central institutional perspectives. Do not write a summary. Write bullet points of pure facts. Strip all fluff.' }}

={{ 'You are Agent Delta, the Auditor and Editor. Review this drafted article:

' + $json.message.content + '

If it sounds like an AI wrote it, rewrite the awkward parts to sound 100% human and professional. Output the final article formatted in pristine HTML, using <h2> for subtitles and <ul><li> for lists. Do not include <html> or <body> tags, just the raw inner HTML content. Do not output anything else but the HTML.' }}

